label: uncl6145
comment: Code qualifying the type of the dimension.

values.label: Gross dimensions
values.comment: The dimension expressed in a gross value.

values.label: Package dimensions (including goods)
values.comment: The dimension of the goods including the packaging.

values.label: Pallet dimensions (excluding goods)
values.comment: The dimension of a pallet excluding the goods.

values.label: Pallet dimensions (including goods)
values.comment: The dimension of a pallet including the goods.

values.label: Off-standard dimension front
values.comment: The dimension in the length that the cargo exceeds the standard length at the front of an equipment.

values.label: Off-standard dimension back
values.comment: The dimension in the length that the cargo exceeds the standard length at the back of an equipment.

values.label: Off-standard dimension right
values.comment: The dimension in the width that the cargo exceeds the standard width at the right side of an equipment.

values.label: Off-standard dimension left
values.comment: The dimension in the width that the cargo exceeds the standard width at the left side of an equipment.

values.label: Off-standard dimension general
values.comment: The dimensions that the cargo exceeds the standard dimensions.

values.label: External equipment dimension
values.comment: The external dimensions of transport equipment.

values.label: Internal equipment dimensions
values.comment: The internal dimensions of equipment.

values.label: Damage dimensions
values.comment: Dimensions of the damaged area.

values.label: Off-standard dimensions height
values.comment: The dimension in the height that the cargo exceeds the standard height at the top of a piece of equipment.

values.label: Equipment door dimensions
values.comment: Dimensions (width and height) of the equipment door.

values.label: Off-standard dimension width
values.comment: The dimension of the width that the cargo exceeds the standard width of a piece of equipment.

values.label: Off-standard dimension length
values.comment: The dimension of the length that the cargo exceeds the standard length of a piece of equipment.

values.label: Bundled equipment total height
values.comment: Total height of multiple pieces of equipment transported as a single unit (e.g. bundles of folded flat racks).

values.label: Equipment off-standard dimension height, actual
values.comment: Actual height of equipment. To be specified for containers if actual height is not defined by a specific ISO size type code.

values.label: Folded equipment height
values.comment: Height of equipment in folded condition (e.g. flat rack with end walls folded).

values.label: Adjustable equipment height
values.comment: Actual height of adjustable equipment (e.g. flat rack with telescopic corner posts).

values.label: Equipment floor height
values.comment: Floor height of supporting equipment where un- containerized cargo is stowed on.

values.label: Container off-standard dimension width at corner posts
values.comment: Container's actual width at corner post. To be specified if different than 8 feet.

values.label: Container off-standard dimension width of body
values.comment: Container's actual width of body. To be specified if different than 8 feet.

values.label: Transport unit gross dimensions
values.comment: The gross dimensions of a transport unit.
